{"word":"G2887 - κόσμιος - kósmios - kos'-mee-os - Of good behaviour","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">κόσμιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">kósmios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">kos'-mee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Of good behaviour</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"யோக்கியதையுள்ள, தகுதியான - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"well - arranged, seemly, modest"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G2889 - κόσμος - kósmos - kos'-mos/2889\">G2889</a> (in its primary sense); <i>orderly</i>, that is, <i>decorous:</i> - of good behaviour, modest.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2885/2885\">G2885</a>, <a href=\"#/G2886/2886\">G2886</a>, <a href=\"#/G2887/2887\">G2887</a>, <a href=\"#/G2889/2889\">G2889</a>"}]}